Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 9
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 37
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 12
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 12
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Isnâ€™t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 6
Author: James Patterson

Description: Two female high school students, Mariko Kumakura and Akko Oohashi, have become a couple. Will they take it public?
Title: GIRL FRIENDS: THE COMPLETE COLLECTION, VOL. 2
Author: Morinaga Milk

Description: A social agency in Italy is taking in young girl and turning them into assassins. Meet their latest: Henrietta, who comes equipped with cybernetic technology.
Title: GUNSLINGER GIRL, OMNIBUS VOL. 6
Author: Yu Aida

Description: All the students at St. Kleio Academy are clones of prominent historical figures.
Title: AFTERSCHOOL CHARISMA, VOL. 7
Author: Kumiko Suekane

Description: The exploration of life on the nineteenth-century Silk Road continues. In this volume, meet Laila and Leily, identical twins on the search for husbands.
Title: A BRIDE'S STORY, VOL. 4
Author: Kaoru Mori

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto
